ActPublic Service Rearrangement and Transfer of Duties Act
SubjectOrder Transfering to Shared Services Canada the Control and Supervision of Certain Portions of the Federal Public Administration in the Department of Public Works and Government Services
PrecisOrder transfering to Shared Services Canada the control and supervision of the following portions of the federal public administration in the Department of Public Works and Government Services known as: (i) the Services Transition and Major Projects Unit, (ii) the Chief Technology Officer Unit, (iii) the Enterprise Services Unit, (iv) the Service Management and Delivery Unit, (v) the Email, Data Centre and Network Services Unit, and (vi) the Email, Data Centre and Network Services Support Unit.
